1.0.0.name: sohelrana820/gchart
1.0.0.description: gChart is s simple PHP calss which provides a perfect and easy way to visualize data on your website using Google Chart library. gChart provides 10 different types of charts (e.g. pie chart, bar chart, geo chart etc) and you can use them for diaplaying of your application report/data.
